      TARPON SPRINGS ROOFING CONTRACTOR<br/><span class="gt">LICENSED & INSURED</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="max-w-2xl mx-auto" style="color:#555555;font-size:1.05rem;line-height:1.75">
      From the historic Sponge Docks to the quiet neighborhoods of Crystal Beach, Tarpon Springs homeowners trust Happy Roof for dependable roof replacement, repair, and installation. We are a licensed and insured roofing contractor serving the entire Tarpon Springs area with high-performance roofing systems built to handle coastal winds, salt air, and Florida's intense summer storms — backed by our 15-year workmanship warranty.
