<!-- WHY HAPPY ROOF IN TARPON SPRINGS -->
<section class="py-20" style="background:#FFFFFF">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-14 items-start">
      <div>
        <p class="sl gt mb-3">Why Happy Roof in Tarpon Springs</p>
        <h2 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);line-height:.95;color:#1A1A1A;letter-spacing:-.01em;margin-bottom:1.5rem">WHY TARPON SPRINGS HOMEOWNERS CHOOSE HAPPY ROOF</h2>
        <p style="color:#555555;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:1.5rem">
          Tarpon Springs is unlike any other city on Florida's Gulf Coast. Known worldwide for its thriving Greek community and the historic Sponge Docks along Dodecanese Boulevard, this waterfront city blends old-world charm with coastal Florida living. Homes here range from century-old bungalows in the historic district to modern construction along Sunset Beach and the communities near Anclote Key. Each neighborhood presents different roofing challenges — from salt air corrosion along the waterfront to wind exposure on elevated lots near the Anclote River.
        </p>
        <p style="color:#555555;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:1.5rem">
          Happy Roof understands the specific demands of roofing in a coastal Pinellas County city. We hold Florida Roofing Contractor License #CCC1337380, carry full general liability and workers' compensation insurance, and pull all required permits with the City of Tarpon Springs and Pinellas County. Whether your home is steps from the Sponge Docks, tucked into the tree-lined streets of the historic district, or out in the neighboring communities of Holiday and Elfers, we deliver consistent quality and stand behind every roof with a 15-year workmanship warranty in writing.
        </p>
        <p style="color:#555555;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:1.5rem">
          The Greek heritage of Tarpon Springs also means many homes feature Mediterranean-style tile roofs that require specialized knowledge to replace and maintain properly. Our crews are experienced with concrete and clay tile systems, barrel tile profiles, and the flashing details these roofs demand. We also install architectural shingles and standing seam metal for homeowners looking for modern performance at a competitive price point.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="scard p-6">
          <div class="check"><div class="check-dot"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg></div><div><strong style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem">15-Year Workmanship Warranty</strong><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.6;margin-top:.25rem">Every Tarpon Springs roof we install comes with a written 15-year workmanship warranty — no exceptions, no fine print.</p></div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="scard p-6">
          <div class="check"><div class="check-dot"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg></div><div><strong style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem">Pinellas County Permits Handled</strong><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.6;margin-top:.25rem">We pull all required permits with the City of Tarpon Springs and Pinellas County and coordinate every inspection from start to finish.</p></div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SERVICES IN TARPON SPRINGS -->
<section class="py-20" style="background:#F7F7F7">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5">
    <div class="text-center mb-14">
      <p class="sl gt mb-3">Our Services</p>
      <h2 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);line-height:.95;color:#1A1A1A;letter-spacing:-.01em">ROOFING SERVICES WE OFFER IN TARPON SPRINGS</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="scard p-8">
        <div style="width:52px;height:52px;border-radius:14px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;background:rgba(230,168,23,.1);margin-bottom:1rem">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="2"><path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.35rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.75rem">Roof Replacement</h3>
        <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">
          Complete tear-off and replacement using Owens Corning Duration HDZ shingles, standing seam metal panels, or concrete and clay tile — including the barrel tile profiles common on Greek-influenced homes near the Sponge Docks. We inspect decking, install premium underlayment and flashing, and handle every permit and county inspection. Most Tarpon Springs shingle roofs are completed in 1 to 3 days.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="scard p-8">
        <div style="width:52px;height:52px;border-radius:14px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;background:rgba(230,168,23,.1);margin-bottom:1rem">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="2"><path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.35rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.75rem">Roof Repair</h3>
        <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">
          From cracked tiles and missing shingles to damaged flashing around chimneys and skylights, we diagnose and repair roofing issues throughout Tarpon Springs. Coastal homes near Sunset Beach and Anclote Key are especially prone to wind-driven rain damage and salt corrosion. We respond quickly after storms and provide honest assessments — if a repair is all you need, that is what we recommend.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="scard p-8">
        <div style="width:52px;height:52px;border-radius:14px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;background:rgba(230,168,23,.1);margin-bottom:1rem">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="2"><path d="M9 21H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h4"/><polyline points="16 17 21 12 16 7"/><line x1="21" y1="12" x2="9" y2="12"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.35rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.75rem">Storm Damage & Insurance</h3>
        <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">
          Tarpon Springs sits directly on the Gulf of Mexico, placing it in one of Florida's most hurricane-vulnerable corridors. When storms hit, we provide thorough damage assessments, document everything for your insurance claim, and coordinate directly with your adjuster. We work with all major insurance carriers in Florida and help Tarpon Springs homeowners navigate the claims process from start to finish.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- OUR PROCESS -->
<section class="py-20" style="background:#FFFFFF">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5">
    <div class="text-center mb-14">
      <p class="sl gt mb-3">How It Works</p>
      <h2 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);line-height:.95;color:#1A1A1A;letter-spacing:-.01em">OUR 4-STEP PROCESS</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <div class="scard p-8 flex gap-5">
        <div class="step-num">1</div>
        <div>
          <h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.2rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.5rem">Free Inspection & Estimate</h3>
          <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">We inspect your roof from top to bottom — checking decking, underlayment, flashing, ventilation, and overall condition. You receive a detailed written estimate with material options, timelines, and transparent pricing. No pressure, no hidden fees.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="scard p-8 flex gap-5">
        <div class="step-num">2</div>
        <div>
          <h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.2rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.5rem">Material Selection & Permits</h3>
          <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">Choose your roofing material and color with our guidance. We pull all permits with the City of Tarpon Springs or Pinellas County, order materials from the manufacturer, and schedule installation on a date that works for you.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="scard p-8 flex gap-5">
        <div class="step-num">3</div>
        <div>
          <h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.2rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.5rem">Professional Installation</h3>
          <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">Our crew performs the full tear-off, inspects and repairs decking as needed, installs new underlayment and flashing, and lays your new roofing system to manufacturer specifications. We protect your landscaping, driveway, and property throughout the process.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="scard p-8 flex gap-5">
        <div class="step-num">4</div>
        <div>
          <h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.2rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.5rem">Final Inspection & Warranty</h3>
          <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">We schedule the county inspection to verify code compliance. Once passed, you receive your warranty documentation — including our 15-year workmanship warranty and manufacturer material warranty. We follow up at 30 days and 1 year.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SERVICE AREA -->
<section class="py-20" style="background:#F7F7F7">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5">
    <div class="text-center mb-10">
      <p class="sl gt mb-3">Tarpon Springs Service Area</p>
      <h2 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);line-height:.95;color:#1A1A1A;letter-spacing:-.01em;margin-bottom:1rem">NEIGHBORHOODS WE SERVE IN TARPON SPRINGS</h2>
      <p style="color:#555555;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.75;max-width:700px;margin:0 auto">Happy Roof provides roofing services throughout the greater Tarpon Springs area and surrounding communities in northern Pinellas County. From the waterfront to the suburbs, we have you covered.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 md:grid-cols-4 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-3 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <span class="scard px-4 py-3 text-center" style="font-size:.9rem;font-weight:600">Sponge Docks</span>
      <span class="scard px-4 py-3 text-center" style="font-size:.9rem;font-weight:600">Historic District</span>
